<db:abstract>
<db:para>Accelerates particles to a vector of the specified magnitude in the specified direction.</db:para>
<db:para>This type was introduced in Qt 6.2.</db:para>
</db:abstract>
<db:pubdate>2024-02-14</db:pubdate>
